                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>At 3:30 p. m. on July 5, Secretary of State Acheson held a news conference at
                    which he made a statement in refutation of allegations of aggression by the
                    Republic of Korea, likening such charges to Nazi claims in 1939 that Poland had
                    started hostilities by attacking Nazi Germany. For the text of the statement,
                    see Department of State <hi rend="italic">Bulletin</hi>, July 17, 1950, page
                    87.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
